{"title":"24mm1.4GM-LensExperience","date":"2019-04-24T14:53:47.000Z","slug":"24mm1-4GM-LensExperience","comments":true,"tags":["24mm","GM大师镜头","人像","定焦","广角镜头","环境人像","索尼"],"categories":["Lens"],"updated":"2019-04-24T15:44:54.077Z","content":"<p><a class=\"headFigure\" href=\"/post/24mm1-4GM-LensExperience\"><img src=\"http://img.zqt0510.cn/19-04-24-c7bb7097831b947694344148ee6020f3.png\" alt=\"截图\"></a></p>\n<h1 id=\"24mm-1-4广角定焦镜头使用体验\"><a href=\"/post/24mm1-4GM-LensExperience\">24mm/1.4广角定焦镜头使用体验</a><a href=\"post/24mm1-4GM-LensExperience#24mm-1-4广角定焦镜头使用体验\"></a></h1><p>索尼G大师镜头FE24mmF1.4GM虽然是一支24mm焦段的广角镜头，但其具备最大F1.4的光圈，并且最近对焦距离为0.24米，所以也非常容易营造出柔美的浅景深，也就是背景虚化效果，而这也是索尼G大师镜头最明显的特色。所以这支镜头不仅仅适合拍摄风光、建筑题材，也很适合拍摄人文以及特写，使用环境非常宽广。<br><a id=\"more\"></a><br><img src=\"http://img.zqt0510.cn/19-04-24-c8d4243cc5487d389f36709f34d380a5.png\" alt=\"截图\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"近距离桌面物件实拍，虚化效果非常讨喜\">近距离桌面物件实拍，虚化效果非常讨喜<a href=\"post/24mm1-4GM-LensExperience#近距离桌面物件实拍，虚化效果非常讨喜\"></a></h4><hr>\n<div class=\"article-img\"><p><img src=\"http://img.zqt0510.cn/19-04-24-d2c70664036f03494deb6f7fdf414627.png\" alt=\"截图\" data-zoomable></p></div>\n<div class=\"article-img\"><p><img src=\"http://img.zqt0510.cn/19-04-24-ad60d7b959c12fc7fc0af690f1140f14.png\" alt=\"截图\" data-zoomable></p></div>\n<div class=\"article-img\"><p><img src=\"http://img.zqt0510.cn/19-04-24-74da4630eb12c8c5f76b2e73dff8c13d.png\" alt=\"截图\" data-zoomable></p></div>\n<div class=\"article-img\"><p><img src=\"http://img.zqt0510.cn/19-04-24-8503134edceedd1a12a1dbfb84ae9792.png\" alt=\"截图\" data-zoomable></p></div>\n<div class=\"article-img\"><p><img src=\"http://img.zqt0510.cn/19-04-24-5d8c0031094d9c5581a9edf4a9e745bd.png\" alt=\"截图\" data-zoomable></p></div>\n<div class=\"article-img\"><p><img src=\"http://img.zqt0510.cn/19-04-24-c802d658e4e2854fa0e4c698e021f75e.png\" alt=\"截图\" data-zoomable></p></div>\n<div class=\"article-img\"><p><img src=\"http://img.zqt0510.cn/19-04-24-7559d1d33504af147f9aa5dfb905ff3d.png\" alt=\"截图\" data-zoomable></p></div>\n<div class=\"article-img\"><p><img src=\"http://img.zqt0510.cn/19-04-24-ae8fe75166d3db7111df3ee8da08e77a.png\" alt=\"截图\" data-zoomable></p></div>\n<h4 id=\"上周末带孩子去学英文课的早上实拍了一些环境人像\">上周末带孩子去学英文课的早上实拍了一些环境人像<a href=\"post/24mm1-4GM-LensExperience#上周末带孩子去学英文课的早上实拍了一些环境人像\"></a></h4><hr>\n<div class=\"article-img\"><p><img src=\"http://img.zqt0510.cn/19-04-24-5b617c3575dd3ab4686a427e74361791.png\" alt=\"截图\" data-zoomable></p></div>\n<div class=\"article-img\"><p><img src=\"http://img.zqt0510.cn/19-04-24-40eed48507291151c788fd0ca5369596.png\" alt=\"截图\" data-zoomable></p></div>\n<h4 id=\"索尼G大师镜头FE24mmF1-4GM大光圈下实拍，前景也能获得柔美的虚化\">索尼G大师镜头FE24mmF1.4GM大光圈下实拍，前景也能获得柔美的虚化<a href=\"post/24mm1-4GM-LensExperience#索尼G大师镜头FE24mmF1-4GM大光圈下实拍，前景也能获得柔美的虚化\"></a></h4><hr>\n<div class=\"article-img\"><p><img src=\"http://img.zqt0510.cn/19-04-24-593487fc5891ee40b0fe60f6eacf0372.png\" alt=\"截图\" data-zoomable></p></div>\n<h4 id=\"光圈收到6-5时也很不错\">光圈收到6.5时也很不错<a href=\"post/24mm1-4GM-LensExperience#光圈收到6-5时也很不错\"></a></h4><hr>\n<h2 id=\"使用总结\">使用总结<a href=\"post/24mm1-4GM-LensExperience#使用总结\"></a></h2><p>可以说，首先在镜头尺寸和重量上，索尼G大师镜头FE 24mm F1.4 GM是一个新的标杆，毕竟在同类型产品中非常突出；其次新镜头进一步扩展了索尼F1.4大光圈定焦镜头的数量，而24mm可以更好地满足星空、风光甚至人文，尤其是两枚XA镜片的加入，能够有效抑制彗形像差，从而精确地再现点光源，使得FE 24mm F1.4 GM成为星空摄影师的拍摄利器。总的来说，索尼FE 24mm F1.4 GM新镜头在保存高素质的同时更发挥了索尼全画幅微单系统便携的优势。</p>\n","next":{"title":"Rose_flower 月季花语","slug":"Rose-flower"},"link":"http://www.zqt0510.cn/post/24mm1-4GM-LensExperience/","toc":[{"title":"<a>24mm/1.4广角定焦镜头使用体验</a>","id":"24mm-1-4广角定焦镜头使用体验","index":"1","children":[{"title":"使用总结","id":"使用总结","index":"1.1"}]}],"copyright":{"author":"Jerry","link":"<a href=\"http://www.zqt0510.cn/post/24mm1-4GM-LensExperience/\" title=\"24mm1.4GM-LensExperience\">http://www.zqt0510.cn/post/24mm1-4GM-LensExperience/</a>","license":"自由转载-非商用-禁止演绎-保持署名 (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}